{
  "stem": "11179.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and we saw my other grandparents at least once a week or so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember we were there for dinner, or lunch, really, which was a major meal.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father's other brother and sister-in-law were there, usually.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember I had-- I remember my grandfather, who passed away when I was only a little over three years old.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I remember him well, because I remember having-- sitting on his lap, and he gave me some food I liked, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember talking with him, from one room to another.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had an extension phone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather did basically the same thing my father did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not sure exactly what, and if was an electrical or was it in steel?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I really don't remember at that time, because it was an earlier time, and electric appliances were pretty new at that time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he did-- he was an advertising salesman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had a big-- they had a big apartment, I remember, and like I said, and I-- I remember talking with him from one to the other, with an extension phone-- the big old phones with the wooden receivers.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- my grandfather's name was Sigfried and Sophie Moser, and the other grandparents, their name was Johanna and Edward Schott, S-C-H-O-T-T.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My earliest Jewish life, I remember, was, of course, the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were not religious, but they were more or less going to the synagogue-- as far as I remember, frequently, but not-- certainly not every week.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not-- they went, to the holy days, at least, they went.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember the synagogue, the people with the high silk hats, still.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember that, when I was li-- when I-- when I was little.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
